<h2>Volunteer Release and Waiver of Liability</h2>

<% if @region.present? %>
  <div class="well" style="font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;">
    <p>This Release and Waiver of Liability executed on <%= Time.zone.today.to_s %>, by <%= current_volunteer.name %> (<%= current_volunteer.email %>) releases liability for <%= @region.title %>, a non-profit corporation, and each of its directors, coordinators, advisers, and employees. The volunteer desires to provide volunteer services for <%= @region.title %> and engage in activities related to serving as a volunteer.</p>

    <p>The volunteer understands the scope of the Volunteer’s relationship with <%= @region.title %> is limited to a volunteer position and that no compensation is expected in return for services provided by the Volunteer; that <%= @region.title %> will not provide any benefits traditionally associated with employment to the Volunteer; and that the Volunteer is responsible for his/her own insurance coverage in the event of personal injury or illness as a result of the Volunteer’s services to <%= @region.title %>.</p>

    <p>1. Waiver and Release: I, the Volunteer, release and forever discharge and hold harmless <%= @region.title %> and its successors and assigns from any and all liability, claims, and demands of whatever kind or nature, either in law or in equity, which arise or may hereafter arise from the services I provide to <%= @region.title %>. I understand and acknowledge that this Release discharges <%= @region.title %> from any liability or claim that I may have against <%= @region.title %> with respect to bodily injury, personal injury, illness, death, or property damage that may result from the services I provide to <%= @region.title %> or occurring while I am providing volunteer services.</p>

    <p>2. Insurance: Further I understand that <%= @region.title %> does not assume any responsibility for or obligation to provide me with financial or other assistance, including but not limited to medical, health, disability benefits or insurance of any nature in the event of my injury, illness, death, or damage to my property. I expressly waive any such claim for compensation or liability on the part of <%= @region.title %> beyond what may be offered freely by <%= @region.title %> in the event of such injury or medical expenses incurred by me.</p>

    <p>3. Use of Personal Vehicle: If using a personal vehicle you must have a valid driver's license and proof of current insurance.  Please note that your personal vehicle insurance must pay if your vehicle is involved in an accident. You may need to check with auto insurance carrier to ensure you are protected in this event. If you are in an accident, please make sure to let <%= @region.title %> as soon as possible, as well as contacting your auto carrier, if needed.</p>

    <p>4. Medical Treatment: I herby Release and forever discharge <%= @region.title %> from any claim whatsoever which arises or may hereafter arise on account of any first-aid treatment or other medical services rendered in connection with an emergency during my tenure as a volunteer with <%= @region.title %>.</p>

    <p>5. Assumption of Risk: I understand that the services I provide to <%= @region.title %> may include activities that may be hazardous to me including, but not limited to, lifting or loading food, riding a bicycle in an urban environment, or operating an automobile. As a volunteer, I hereby expressly assume the risk of injury or harm from these activities and release <%= @region.title %> from all liability for injury, illness, death, or property damge resulting from the services I provide as a volunteer or occurring while I providing volunteer services.</p>

    <p>By signing below, I hereby warrant that I over the age of 18, or legally emancipated, and I express my complete understanding of all terms and conditions of this agreement, and I enter into this release and waiver of liability willingly and voluntarily.</p>
  </div>
  <% unless current_volunteer.waiver_signed %>
    <%= form_tag("/waiver") do %>
      Check to sign electronically: <%= check_box_tag 'accept', 1 %>
      <br />
      Date: <%= Time.zone.today.to_s %>
      <br />
      <br />
      <%= submit_tag 'Sign', class: "form-control" %>
    <% end %>
  <% else %>
    <span style="font-weight: bold; color: orange;">
      You signed the waiver at <%= current_volunteer.waiver_signed_at.to_s %>.
    </span>
  <% end %>
<% else %>
  <p>You are not currently assigned to a region for volunteering. Please contact your regional volunteer coordinator to be assigned! If that fails to work, try Hana at <a href="mailto:admin@tcfoodjustice.org?subject=Veggietables Volunteer Assignment for ...">admin@tcfoodjustice.org</a> to be assigned to your region. Thanks for joining!</p>

<% end %>
